<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://accounts.google.com/gsi/client" async defer></script>
    <script src="../JavaScript/studentLogin.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/stduentLogin.css" />
    <title>로그인 페이지</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="title">SIGN-IN</h1>
    <form action="/studentId" method="post">
      <h2>SIGN-IN</h2>
      <p>예약하시기 전에 로그인을 해주세요</p>
      <div class="container">
        <input type="text" name="student_id" id="student_id" placeholder="학번을 입력해주세요" autofocus required maxlength="5" pattern="[0-9]{5}" />
        <div id="g_id_onload" data-client_id="297700983813-6bcnrhkujdtt7sbk4ai0e9jhr90kommk.apps.googleusercontent.com" data-login_uri="http://localhost:3000/studentLogin" data-auto_prompt="false">
        </div>
        <div class="g_id_signin" data-type="standard" data-size="large" data-theme="outline" data-text="sign_in_with" data-shape="rectangular" data-logo_alignment="left">
        </div>
        <button type="submit">Sign in</button>
      </div>
      <div class="blueContainer"></div>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>